0.8.name: wordpress/document-gallery
0.8.description:
This plugin allows the user to effortlessly include a gallery, much like a photo gallery, of all your non-image attachments anywhere within your post.

The plugin will, by default, inherit the styling within your active theme, but with a little CSS knowledge it is easily modified to meet your specific needs.

Read more in the Installation tab!

Developers

Document Gallery includes features intended to make integrating the plugin into the core of your theme or plugin very convenient. See the bottom of the Installation tab for specific documentation on the various features included.

If this plugin has helped you, please take a moment to rate it!
